1
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:05,200
Come with me.

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:13,540
Where can I go with you without money?

3
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:17,400
Eat dirt with you?

4
00:00:25,720 --> 00:00:26,920
Do you trust me?

5
00:00:31,560 --> 00:00:33,120
I know a way to make money.

6
00:00:33,520 --> 00:00:35,320
It can get us out of here quickly.

7
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:36,960
Doing what?

8
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:41,500
Find the place with the most rich people.

9
00:00:42,120 --> 00:00:43,960
Is this a bad idea?

10
00:00:44,280 --> 00:00:46,600
Do you really not want to leave with me?

11
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:58,080
Mr. Huang, Yong.

12
00:00:58,960 --> 00:00:59,880
Go keep Yong company.

13
00:00:59,880 --> 00:01:00,880
Mr. Huang.

14
00:01:01,120 --> 00:01:01,760
Come.

15
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:03,360
How is this?

16
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:05,880
I saved her especially for you.

17
00:01:05,880 --> 00:01:07,080
It's her first day.

18
00:01:07,080 --> 00:01:07,920
Go.

19
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:09,120
Sit next to Mr. Huang.

20
00:01:09,720 --> 00:01:10,800
I swear to you,

21
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:13,580
she really just started her first day today.

22
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:15,760
What are you waiting for?

23
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:18,080
Jiajia, pour Mr. Huang a drink.

24
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:20,240
Mr. Huang, here's to you.

25
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,240
Mr. Huang.

26
00:01:25,720 --> 00:01:27,580
Mr. Huang, let me toast you again.

27
00:01:33,039 --> 00:01:34,120
Jiajia.

28
00:01:35,520 --> 00:01:36,320
Jiajia.

29
00:01:36,320 --> 00:01:39,479
Mr. Huang, Yong, this is our top girl.

30
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:40,800
Boss Huang.

31
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:42,640
Calm down.

32
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:43,479
Come.

33
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:59,160
Everyone, listen to me.

34
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:03,240
We have our top sales champion of the week again.

35
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:05,840
It's Na again.

36
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:09,199
She opened another bottle of Louis XIII tonight.

37
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,640
Congratulations, Na.

38
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:13,720
It's 1 a.m. now.

39
00:02:13,720 --> 00:02:14,980
You must all be hungry.

40
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:17,890
Na will treat you to a late-night snack later.

41
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,440
Looking for prey.

42
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,500
Still haven't chosen?

43
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,400
I'm not very good at picking.

44
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,700
I'm exhausted.

45
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:52,079
Na, thank you for the dress.

46
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,560
I got my first deal today.

47
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,820
Congratulations. I was right, wasn't I?

48
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:57,640
Show off your strengths,

49
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:59,040
and you got a deal.

50
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:06,800
What?

51
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,260
You want to see?

52
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,800
Come here.

53
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,660
Put it on and let me see.

54
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,840
Try it on.

55
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,840
Na, I really envy you.

56
00:03:27,760 --> 00:03:30,560
I wish I had half your ability to make money.

57
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:34,280
You are young and beautiful.

58
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:35,900
It's only a matter of time.

59
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:40,440
In this line of work, you'll get the hang of it after a while.

60
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,480
Na.

61
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:50,160
I heard you also sublet apartments.

62
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,480
I just wanted to ask

63
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:54,920
if you have any rooms available to sublet.

64
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,360
Don't we have dorms here?

65
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:00,080
Why spend that money?

66
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:02,680
I live with my boyfriend.

67
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,320
You have a boyfriend?

68
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:09,840
Take your time.

69
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,680
Yes, Na.

70
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:13,370
I washed your skirt and am returning it to you.

71
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:18,040
I told you I was giving it to you. Keep it.

72
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:19,760
No need, Na.

73
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:21,820
I don't really like owing people.

74
00:04:21,880 --> 00:04:24,410
Besides, I'll buy my own once I start working.

75
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:27,170
Quite the personality.

76
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:36,280
We're here.

77
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,280
This neighborhood

78
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:50,440
is a bit remote,

79
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:51,840
but it's quiet.

80
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:55,290
Since we work night shifts, we can sleep more during the day.

81
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:57,640
Your place is quite cozy.

82
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:01,320
This is a small storage room.

83
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:03,200
Over here is my bedroom.

84
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:08,160
This is the walk-in closet.

85
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:12,200
It's also where I spend most of my time.

86
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:15,640
Who is it?

87
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:18,100
It should be my boyfriend.

88
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,490
I told you about him.

89
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:22,160
You didn't tell me he was coming.

90
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:24,320
Since we're going to live together,

91
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:25,920
he had to come and take a look.

92
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:26,880
Wait.

93
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:30,520
You're paying the rent. Do you still need his permission?

94
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,700
What are you thinking?

95
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:34,560
Coming!

96
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,360
Secure the scene.

97
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,560
Who are you?

98
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,480
Ma Guodong.

99
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:06,240
They all call me Old Ma.

100
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:08,200
You can call me Captain Ma.

101
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,120
I know you.

102
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:14,440
Lin Wei, the top student who just graduated from the police academy.

103
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:35,040
The killer is a habitual offender with criminal experience.

104
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:37,120
There is no damage to the doors and windows.

105
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:39,320
There are no obvious signs of a struggle in the room.

106
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:43,400
And the killer cleaned up before leaving the scene.

107
00:06:43,840 --> 00:06:45,040
One thing is certain.

108
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:46,720
These two female victims

109
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:51,400
must have worked in entertainment venues like nightclubs.

110
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:52,360
How do you know?

111
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,200
A 24-inch large color TV.

112
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,640
XO liquor.

113
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:56,640
And in the closet,

114
00:06:56,760 --> 00:07:00,280
there are mini skirts and ultra-short skirts in all colors.

115
00:07:00,280 --> 00:07:02,160
What normal girl dresses like this?

116
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,360
Including this perfume. I saw it in the mall,

117
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:06,200
it sells for at least a few hundred yuan.

118
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,760
Women working in offices

119
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:09,200
or factories

120
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,800
couldn't afford it.

121
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,720
Where is the nearest nightclub?

122
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:14,400
The landlord's statement is done.

123
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:15,720
The tenant's name is Li Na.

124
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,920
She should be one of the victims.

125
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,650
She works at Qianye Nightclub.

126
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:25,560
Nana is our top liquor saleswoman.

127
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,520
Where is she?

128
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:28,650
She asked for leave.

129
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:31,160
Today or yesterday?

130
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,960
It was yesterday.

131
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:34,360
Yesterday.

132
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:36,960
Check if anyone else is missing.

133
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,920
Look at each other.

134
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,320
Is anyone else missing?

135
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,560
No one else?

136
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,460
Linda seems to be missing too.

137
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,840
Do you have a picture of Linda?

138
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:49,640
Liu Qing,

139
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,680
cooperate with the officer.

140
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,210
Go check the dressing room.

141
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,000
Okay.

142
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:56,960
One bottle of Sister Na's perfume equals my monthly income.

143
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:58,320
I'm just a newbie.

144
00:07:58,320 --> 00:07:59,960
Sister Na usually guides us.

145
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:01,560
She's pretty good to all of us.

146
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:03,420
Customers like to give her gifts.

147
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:05,240
She also sublets apartments.

148
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:08,200
Her income is one of the highest around here.

149
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:10,320
No, Officer.

150
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,240
I think

151
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:14,960
I need to know exactly what happened.

152
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,200
Look,

153
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:18,000
all the girls are here.

154
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:20,600
This is a normal, legal entertainment venue, right?

155
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,760
We didn't kill anyone,

156
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:22,720
or commit arson.

157
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,720
If you keep investigating like this...

158
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:25,960
Li Na is dead. It's a homicide.

159
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:29,920
Do you think I should investigate it or not?

160
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:33,120
Officer Lin, Captain Ma, the forensic report is out.

161
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,039
Copy that.

162
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:35,840
Tell Officer Lin

163
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:37,600
to return to the station immediately.

164
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,320
Okay, copy.

165
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,100
I'll wait for you downstairs.

166
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,480
Bro, got a light?

167
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:03,720
A Zippo.

168
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:05,050
You know your stuff.

169
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,840
What's going on in there?

170
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:13,480
Routine check.

171
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,320
It's an emergency,

172
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,680
so I won't waste time.

173
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,840
Everyone met yesterday.

174
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:23,480
Yeah.

175
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,600
This is Comrade Lin Wei,

176
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,520
our new comrade.

177
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:26,400
Hello, everyone.

178
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:27,000
Lin Wei,

179
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:30,400
please brief everyone on the basic facts of this case.

180
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:33,500
There are currently two victims.

181
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:36,200
Both suffered varying degrees of abuse before death.

182
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,480
The time of death is roughly the same,

183
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,800
but the cause of death is completely different.

184
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:40,720
Li Na died from mechanical asphyxiation.

185
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:42,680
Linda was assaulted before death

186
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:44,520
and died from a blow to the back of the head.

187
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:47,480
Judging from the characteristics of the injuries on the victims' bodies,

188
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,600
it was not done by a single person.

189
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,000
It should be a gang crime.

190
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:52,800
Ma,

191
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,440
do you have any progress on your end?

192
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,240
Li Na called in sick yesterday.

193
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:59,080
Nothing else particularly useful.

194
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,880
How is the investigation into her social relations?

195
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:02,680
We are screening them one by one.

196
00:10:05,800 --> 00:10:07,860
The nature of this case is egregious.

197
00:10:07,920 --> 00:10:09,800
The leadership takes it very seriously,

198
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:11,600
and asked us to set up a special task force.

199
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:12,720
We must solve it as soon as possible.

200
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:13,850
Meeting adjourned.

201
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:17,960
Come in quickly, you two.

202
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,440
What's your name?

203
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,060
What do you do for a living?

204
00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:32,010
Sister Na, just call him Huazi.

205
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,080
He is currently unemployed.

206
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:37,720
Living off your girlfriend?

207
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,680
Quite capable.

208
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:42,330
Sister Na, he's just like that.

209
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:44,480
Are the kitchen and bathroom over here?

210
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:45,400
Show me around.

211
00:10:50,800 --> 00:10:52,200
The kitchen isn't very big.

212
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,730
But it's enough for you two.

213
00:10:53,920 --> 00:10:55,720
The bathroom is right next to it.

214
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:58,480
That's the whole apartment.

215
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,320
What do you think?

216
00:11:02,040 --> 00:11:03,040
It's pretty good.

217
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:04,080
Alright.

218
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:05,900
Then it's settled.

219
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:09,840
Xiaojia.

220
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,610
I don't mean to lecture you.

221
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:15,000
But your boyfriend is pretty awful.

222
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:23,130
Who let you into my bedroom?

223
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:26,520
Do you have any manners?

224
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:28,920
Why are you touching other people's stuff?

225
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:30,620
Unbelievable.

226
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:33,980
Jiajia, I don't want to rent this place anymore.

227
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:38,020
What are you doing?

228
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:40,530
Nothing. I just wanted to make you shut up.

229
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:42,320
Jiajia.

230
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:45,880
What does this mean?
